      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, remains in showroom state. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new factory delivery, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality for the discerning driver.",
