    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this absolute stunner! It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d honestly think it just rolled right off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new and has been loved every mile of the way, this is the one for you! Come take a look and fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
