      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is mechanically impeccable, showcasing a linear power band and crisp throttle response facilitated by its six individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis is structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe, a critical upgrade for maintaining torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing fresh bushings and dampers to preserve the sharp turn-in and communicative steering feel this platform is known for. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, with no evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
